//////Local Dependency
> Local to the folder
> Can only be used in the same folder
> Added to package.json
> All dependency should/try to go local

/////global Dependency
> Install in laptop node_modules rather than folder
> It is not added in package.json
> it can be used for any application
> only packages that help to generate/run the app
> need admin permissions

/////dev Dependency
> Same like Local Dependency
> Only difference is of the json object

///////Step to Install Global Dependency
# Windows
(Only One Time)
> Open cmd as admin
> npm i -g packagename

# Mac/linux
(Only One Time)
> open terminal
> sudo npm i -g packagename

///////Step to Install Dev Dependency
> open Cmd
> npm i --save-dev packagename

